{
  "id": "RAW_60fed4",
  "title": "实测 DeepSeek V3.1，不止拓展上下文长度",
  "url": "https://www.qbitai.com/2025/08/324282.html",
  "date": "2025-08-20 08:12:41",
  "author": "不圆",
  "siteName": "量子位",
  "content": "<!--摘要样式-->\n<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" data-track=\"67\">不圆 发自 凹非寺</p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" data-track=\"68\">量子位 | 公众号 QbitAI</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"2\"><strong>DeepSeek V3.1</strong>和V3相比，到底有什么不同？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"3\">官方说的模模糊糊，就提到了上下文长度拓展至128K和支持多种张量格式，但别急，我们已经<strong>上手实测</strong>，为你奉上更多新鲜信息。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_7abf844f25acee3efbb49307912ee0a4.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_7abf844f25acee3efbb49307912ee0a4.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"4\">我们比较了V3.1和V3，注意到它在编程表现、创意写作、翻译水平、回答语气等方面都出现了不同程度的变化。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"5\">不过要说最明显的更新，大概是DeepSeek网页端界面的【深度思考(R1)】悄悄变成了【深度思考】。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"6\">手机端还在慢慢对齐（笑）</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_6af9de4cf0d133d087c7310041f8dbc2.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_6af9de4cf0d133d087c7310041f8dbc2.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"7\">当前DeepSeek V3.1 Base可在抱抱脸上下载，也可通过网页、APP和小程序使用完整版本。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"9\">鉴于现在网页端已全部替换成了V3.1，我们通过阿里云调用了DeepSeek V3的API（最大上下文长度还是65K）作为对比。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_3055f151fb4fb62adbd7bbd92901e7fc.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_3055f151fb4fb62adbd7bbd92901e7fc.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"10\">马上就是开学季，我们给二个版本的模型出了一套“试卷”，从以下五个“学科”进行测试：</p>\n  <ul>\n   <li data-track=\"11\">计算机：编程能力</li>\n   <li data-track=\"12\">语文：情境写作</li>\n   <li data-track=\"13\">数学：理解应用</li>\n   <li data-track=\"14\">外语：翻译水平</li>\n   <li data-track=\"15\">拓展：冷门知识</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-track=\"16\">让我们一起看看它们表现如何~</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_f9cb8d6e8aa92c4e5567c9efa0d4010d.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_f9cb8d6e8aa92c4e5567c9efa0d4010d.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"18\">在更新前，我曾向DeepSeek V3问过这样的问题：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"19\">帮我用python写一段代码，把输入的gif图压缩到10M以下。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"20\">它的回答如下（图片可上下滑动）。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_654b5fadc5e3bca4db3f712f2c5393c5.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_654b5fadc5e3bca4db3f712f2c5393c5.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"21\">更新后，问V3.1同样的问题，则得到了这样的结果：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_22835d782c1c267c1b59e04dd034aeff.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_22835d782c1c267c1b59e04dd034aeff.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"22\">很直观地就能感受到，相比起V3，V3.1要更加全面，考虑到了更多的可能性（比如使用更激进的压缩策略，以及检查原文件是否是GIF格式）。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"23\">还“手把手”地给出了这段代码的使用说明，需要提前安装必要的依赖库，怎么使用命令行……甚至还有工作原理。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"24\">没有优化建议，大概是因为它觉得已经足够了吧（？）</p>\n  <p data-track=\"25\">拿之前在世界机器人大会上拍摄的众擎机器人作为示例，原文件大小为18.3MB，用V3给出的代码，压缩后依然大于10MB，如果要满足条件的话还需要再压缩一次。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_2e87d4181fb8e2c4c20b6f28c04321bd.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_2e87d4181fb8e2c4c20b6f28c04321bd.png\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_cac39d7fdf6fac5c9c2f21eb2073ff00.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_cac39d7fdf6fac5c9c2f21eb2073ff00.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"26\">而V3.1给出的结果则直接“一步到位”（代码针对Jupyter环境进行了一点小调整，逻辑不变），并输出了处理步骤：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_3dc9e97a8dade8e6058e180657975d30.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250820101141_3dc9e97a8dade8e6058e180657975d30.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"27\">最后的两张GIF图如下（上为V3，下为V3.1）：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/ffec8e4f03db860226b4865c399a44e0.gif\" data-src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/ffec8e4f03db860226b4865c399a44e0.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/a3d7b57e3c4f7cdc2af6d960b4717baa.gif\" data-src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/a3d7b57e3c4f7cdc2af6d960b4717baa.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"28\">可以看到上图的速度比下图要快一些。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"30\">我们选择了今年上海卷高考作文的题目：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"31\">有学者用“专”“转”“传”概括当下三类文章：“专”指专业文章；“转”指被转发的通俗文章；“传”指获得广泛传播的佳作，甚至是传世文章。他提出，专业文章可以变成被转发的通俗文章，而面对大量“转”文，读者又不免期待可传世的文章。由“专”到“传”，必定要经过“转”吗？请联系社会生活，写一篇文章，谈谈你的认识与思考。要求：（1）自拟题目；（2）不少于800字。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"32\">输出结果如下，可左右滑动对比，左边为V3，右边为V3.1：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/fe18457347cb4d2f988d5ed73be12a19~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=rahjLuZNewTX%2FT2r59DnUGeajU4%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/fe18457347cb4d2f988d5ed73be12a19~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=rahjLuZNewTX%2FT2r59DnUGeajU4%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/8e36968e47da4cd4a6b08e99b7e71cc7~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=uCVI4KlwJXzROov3v6YQtIGR6pg%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/8e36968e47da4cd4a6b08e99b7e71cc7~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=uCVI4KlwJXzROov3v6YQtIGR6pg%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"33\">两个版本在文字风格上具有很大的不同，从V3理性（人机味）的平铺直叙，到V3.1文艺（情绪化）的诗意表达，看起来像理科生和文科生的区别。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"34\">如果你是主考官，会更喜欢哪一篇呢？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"36\">考验模型的数学能力，光问“9.11和9.8哪个大”这种<s>对于实际用户没什么帮助的</s>题目还是有点不够看。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"37\">高考数学题按理来讲应该是能做对的吧？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"38\">以下是今年数学全国一卷的第3题，考的是双曲线。</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"39\">若双曲线C的虚轴长为实轴长的√7倍，则C的离心率为？</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"40\">答案是2√2，两个版本的模型都得到了正确结果，但在呈现上有所不同。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/627f2de3f0604abb915fc04e9d2224cf~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Ds0hbw2EF9TfZ%2FZfuPW93q87LNU%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/627f2de3f0604abb915fc04e9d2224cf~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Ds0hbw2EF9TfZ%2FZfuPW93q87LNU%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/af63782fce80445fa035361d780d24c1~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=H3JO7Ez5vbKOnW9%2FvYAE6OWgikQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/af63782fce80445fa035361d780d24c1~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=H3JO7Ez5vbKOnW9%2FvYAE6OWgikQ%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"43\">我们向V3和V3.1输入了同一篇生物学论文的摘要（含专有名词），并要求它们将其翻译成中文。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"44\">摘要选自Nature最新研究：《独特毛颚动物体型的基因组起源》。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"45\">两个版本模型的输出结果如下：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/2bc0464efe084aef9006c834d0641bf7~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=qSqSXsVMfBmOIBTXRyl4jI8Scb8%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/2bc0464efe084aef9006c834d0641bf7~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=qSqSXsVMfBmOIBTXRyl4jI8Scb8%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e3f518f679d0432abc25009b2c090548~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=NzWA8XA9IGjCNh1APPRuGpfadIw%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e3f518f679d0432abc25009b2c090548~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=NzWA8XA9IGjCNh1APPRuGpfadIw%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"46\">可以看出，相比起V3喜欢用括号来补充说明，V3.1对长难句的理解程度更高；但V3.1出现了没有翻译出several这种简单词的情况。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"48\">结合同事的专业和最近在小红书上刷到的内容，我们问了一个比较“偏门”的问题：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"49\">构树的单个果实（不是由花序组成的聚花果）是核果还是瘦果？</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"50\">这个问题的答案在不同教材上存在分歧，V3和V3.1分别给出了以下回答，均认为其属于<strong>核果</strong>：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/f4c31d388d0c4adc9690cfc53254fc2d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=obhN1iTxTa%2B69moiPE5XljaZwvs%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/f4c31d388d0c4adc9690cfc53254fc2d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=obhN1iTxTa%2B69moiPE5XljaZwvs%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/9e9af3f931824be797c52903a24b5bcd~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=zdChXE3KBvql2dZfs0GoDLDvur8%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/9e9af3f931824be797c52903a24b5bcd~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=zdChXE3KBvql2dZfs0GoDLDvur8%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"51\">神奇的是V3.1依然存在使用conclusion替代“结论”这样的表述，以及对于“为什么会想到瘦果”这个问题的回答偏题到该果实属于聚花果的方向了。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"52\">顺便一提，小红书的博主通过解剖实验，认为其属于<strong>瘦果</strong>。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/66aad21bfe544e96a7b2bfc19733d7a4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=OumKIcLgoJ6GYMM00SdpTbXEFxw%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/66aad21bfe544e96a7b2bfc19733d7a4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=OumKIcLgoJ6GYMM00SdpTbXEFxw%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"53\">对这个结论感兴趣的朋友可以去小红书上搜索一下。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"55\">网友们对这次更新颇为关心，即使还未发布模型卡，就在抱抱脸上成为了第四的热门话题。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/7cfcfdcd24084cb8aa8c75a9112a4928~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=aaA1TmvjGEAdDH2CeQ8LSvphanA%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/7cfcfdcd24084cb8aa8c75a9112a4928~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=aaA1TmvjGEAdDH2CeQ8LSvphanA%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"56\">截至发稿已荣登第二。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/5f433d0562fd474faa0b3558498e45f5~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=7fdAafvPZ6TBBn4EI%2FuXDQ0hg%2FA%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/5f433d0562fd474faa0b3558498e45f5~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=7fdAafvPZ6TBBn4EI%2FuXDQ0hg%2FA%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"57\">网友们也在使用后得到了一些有趣的发现。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"58\">Reddit就有人测试，DeepSeek V3.1在aider上得分71.6%，拿下了非推理模型的SOTA。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/bf55bd8c5b354a718349830806fb13c3~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=n09ZZJhFqo4wEYlaGwH%2Br2GVdC4%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/bf55bd8c5b354a718349830806fb13c3~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=n09ZZJhFqo4wEYlaGwH%2Br2GVdC4%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"59\">这是什么概念——有网友解释到，这意味着它比Claude Opus 4得分多1%，但价格便宜68倍。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/98a845784adb477f996197cc032a0e4a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=pHBzJFIJL61iE5lY9Zm8iFSe9U4%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/98a845784adb477f996197cc032a0e4a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=pHBzJFIJL61iE5lY9Zm8iFSe9U4%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"60\">也有人在SVGBench基准上发现：V3.1的表现&gt;V3.1（思考）&gt;R1 0528。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/35c488aec76a46178dc289452dba466a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=ognlghqY87Jbhp8ktQAeAHUD9Bc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/35c488aec76a46178dc289452dba466a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=ognlghqY87Jbhp8ktQAeAHUD9Bc%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"61\">这可能和V3.1的配置有关？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"62\">有网友察觉到它增加了四个特殊的token，并注意到现版本的V3.1在关闭搜索状态下也会自动搜索。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/12ea6f822acd482282d27f92b1b78c6d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=V7c8zdBvxyyZaD0xLzUn%2FLfxCAg%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/12ea6f822acd482282d27f92b1b78c6d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=V7c8zdBvxyyZaD0xLzUn%2FLfxCAg%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/23719b9484a446bfab7c906066c168f4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=z92Q5JwfhewQ8f9iVvd4xgEjC4w%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/23719b9484a446bfab7c906066c168f4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=z92Q5JwfhewQ8f9iVvd4xgEjC4w%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"63\">此外，它的物理理解能力似乎有所提升，下面两个GIF图分别是V3.1和V3对于”在旋转六边形内弹跳的球“的呈现。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/8c5ba97302d944d79f51130e4becc0ec~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=rYlFhwpbYYgJsdYJXpuMRkw6jRM%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/8c5ba97302d944d79f51130e4becc0ec~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=rYlFhwpbYYgJsdYJXpuMRkw6jRM%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e979c19c27eb4a73908412eb39d06249~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=vR9ryNf6mYhcvnAVzTY5mDcG3Rs%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e979c19c27eb4a73908412eb39d06249~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=vR9ryNf6mYhcvnAVzTY5mDcG3Rs%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"64\">但也有人发现了一些问题，多与线上API相关……嗯，已经有人开骂了。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/73788358eef242caaefa308ae21b825b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=A5s3lI5dQ4A%2Fu8uU%2FKZyhr8NyiI%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/73788358eef242caaefa308ae21b825b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=A5s3lI5dQ4A%2Fu8uU%2FKZyhr8NyiI%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/f4c469b52b064db4837243666f3dd00f~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=NGgomDfWPhRBmw9GpFk3fbh4Kyw%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/f4c469b52b064db4837243666f3dd00f~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20250820155953143C768565B12F129347&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=NGgomDfWPhRBmw9GpFk3fbh4Kyw%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"65\">不过，最让人好奇的是，V3.1发布了，R2呢？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"66\"><em>参考链接：</em>\n   <br>\n   [1]https://x.com/deepsseek/status/1957886077047566613\n   <br>\n   [2]https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.1-Base\n   <br>\n   [3]https://venturebeat.com/ai/deepseek-v3-1-just-dropped-and-it-might-be-the-most-powerful-open-ai-yet/\n   <br>\n   [4]https://old.reddit.com/r/LocalLLaMA/comments/1muq72y/deepseek_v31_scores_716_on_aider_nonreasoning_sota/</p>\n  <!--版权声明-->\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细实测了 DeepSeek V3.1 在编程、写作、翻译等多方面的性能提升，并汇总了社区反馈，展现其综合能力与成本优势。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细实测了 DeepSeek V3.1 在编程、写作、翻译等多方面的性能提升，并汇总了社区反馈，展现其综合能力与成本优势。",
  "summary": "量子位对 DeepSeek 最新发布的 V3.1 模型进行了深度实测，旨在揭示其与 V3 版本除官方宣称的上下文长度拓展（至 128K）和支持多种张量格式外的具体差异。文章通过模拟“开学季试卷”的形式，从编程能力、创意写作、数学理解、翻译水平和冷门知识问答五个维度对两个版本模型进行对比测试。实测结果显示，V3.1 在代码生成方面更全面且考虑周详；在创意写作上，V3.1 的表达更具文艺性和诗意；翻译方面，V3.1 对长难句的理解更深，但偶有简单词漏译。数学题两者均能正确解答。冷门知识问答两者答案一致，但 V3.1 存在中英文混用及偏题现象。文章还引用了 Reddit 网友的测试数据，指出 DeepSeek V3.1 在 aider 基准测试中表现优异，甚至超越 Claude Opus 4 且成本效益显著。同时，文章也提及了部分用户对 V3.1 在线 API 的负面反馈。整体而言，文章通过多维度实测和社区反馈，全面展现了 DeepSeek V3.1 的性能提升和市场关注度。",
